  <description>
    <p>
      Showdown is a simple application for rendering and viewing
      Markdown files.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>GitHub inspired default stylesheet</li>
      <li>Table of contents navigation</li>
      <li>Integrated search bar</li>
      <li>Custom user stylesheets and scripts</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
